page.title: 19I'm new to Slyne-with- Hest
page.content: This year I have moved into Slyne-with Hest.We live in three old cottages knocked into one.The middle one was the village reading room.The actual cottages date back to the 1700's but the outhouses we have date to about the 1500's.I personally like it in Slyne with Hest because it is peaceful and near the sea and the hills but it's also near the town of Lancaster and the M6 motorway.All my family like Slyne with Hest as there are lots of fields and lanes to walk down.Also I like bird spotting and alot of birds come to the shore at Hest bank.I go to Slyne with Hest Church of England School.I like it there.I have moved many times before but I really think I will enjoy living here in Slyne-with-Hest. Andrew Brownlow.
